Truck felt off a few days ago so I decided to take a look. And the bolt on my stabilizer bat bushing was completely gone. Back end was stripped out so I had to remove the bumper and go from the opposite side to put a nut on the back side of the bolt. Actual repair took 5 minutes. Removing the grill guard, grill and bumper took up majority of the time. Decided to go ahead and swap out the headlights since I had the whole front torn down anyway.  #Chevrolet #chevy #1999suburban #chevytrucks #classictrucks #classicchevy #restore #rebuild #diy
